Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Cut chicken fillets into bite size pieces (or leave whole, if desired). Place chicken in a 9 x 13 inch pan, and put cheese slices on top. Spread mushroom soup over all. Mix stuffing according to package directions, and place on top of chicken dish. Bake uncovered for 1 hour at 350 degrees F (175 degrees C).